<section>
  <div class="container  custom-container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 class="text-center card-title">Professional Loan for CA, CS, Doctors, Architects, and other professionals</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="container custom-application">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p>Please provide following details for the application</p>
      <%= form_for @professional_loan, :url => { :action => "professional_loan" }, remote: false, html: { class: "custom_personal_loan" } do |f| %>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <label>Your Full Name</label>
              <%= f.text_field(:full_name, class: "form-control", autofocus: "true") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <label>Your Mobile Number</label>
              <%= f.number_field(:mobile_number, class: "form-control") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <label>Your Email</label>
              <%= f.text_field(:email, class: "form-control") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <label>Your Purpose</label>
              <%= f.select(:loan_purpose, @professional_loan.loan_reasons, class: "form-control") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-custom btn-block">Submit</button>
          <br>
          <p class="text-center"><span style="color: blue;">Click on this link to apply directly.</span> <%= link_to "Apply", professional_loan_path('step1'), method: :get, style: "color: #0000ff; font-weight: 500;" %></p><br>
      <%end%>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h4 class="crd-heading">
        <br>
        <span>Are you looking to apply for a professional loan?</span><br><br>
        GrowwCapital is @ your service to ensure you procure it from the best bank and which meets all financial requirements of your business. Fill the form & send it. You can also call us on <a href="tel:+918806644344">+91-88066-44344</a>.
      </h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="credit-card-banks owl-carousel">
        <% ProfessionalLoanBank.all.uniq.each do |card| %>
          <div class="part-img-effect"><%= image_tag url_for(card.bank_image), width: 200, height: 100 %></div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
</div>
<div class="container application-description">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <br>
      <p class="pl-ser"><strong>Professional Loan Details</strong></p>
      <div class="row table-responsive">
        <table class="table">
          <tr>
            <td>Interest Rate</td>
            <td>10.50% Onwards</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Processing Fee</td>
            <td>Up to 2% on loan amt.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Loan Period</td>
            <td>5 years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Lowest EMI per lac</td>
            <td>2149 for 5 years</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>Chartered Accountants, Company Secretaries, Doctors, & Architects are the standard four types of professionals who are eligible to apply for professional loans. All the leading banks have provision for these loans. Some banks also accommodate more in the category of professionals. When you talk to us and give us a brief on your profile and requirements we can present the right options to you.</p>
      <p>All such professional may apply for these loans for various needs, starting from setting up their offices or meet long and short term professional goals. Like already mentioned some banks also provide loans to salaried and non-individuals such as diagnostic centers and hospitals.</p>
      <p>If you belong to any of the above professions and seek loan, we can help you get it within a short span of time and minimum paperwork and running around. Our team has helped many professionals to get a quick approval and disbursement of their loan amount.</p>
      <p>Different <b>interest rates</b> are charged for loans to different professionals. We will provide you with detailed information during the discussion. Interest rate charged for doctor’s loan may vary between 14% to 16% p.a. whereas CAs are offered professional loans at 16% and above p.a. Upper and lower limit of loan may differ from bank to bank. We will also give you information regarding balance transfer and whether you or the bank will bear the loan closure charges if you wish to close it before time.</p>
      <p>Some banks also facilitate <b>collateral free funding</b> of loans. Based on qualifications and other criteria some banks also offer instant professional loan facility. Professional loans come in the category of unsecured loans.</p>
      <p>If you’re a doctors (MD, MBBS, BAMS, BHMS, MDS, BDS and Veterinary, plus Physiotherapists) you can apply for this loan. Some banks also offer professional loans to engineers, chartered accountants, company secretaries and architects. As well as diagnostic centers, clinics, hospitals, private limited company, proprietorship and partnership firms, closely held limited companies, etc. If you belong to any of the above brackets, do get in touch with us. We shall present the best options.</p>
      <p class="pl-ser">Documentations</p>
      <p>Documentations required for this loan are different for different categories of professionals. <b>Salaried class</b> seeking the loan will be required to produce photo identity and address proof, KYC as defined by RBI, education proof, previous 3 months bank statement, residence ownership proof, etc. These may slightly differ from bank to bank.</p>
      <p><b>Self Employed professionals</b> viz. Hospitals, Diagnostic centers are required to submit photo identity and address proof, KYC as defined by RBI, education proof, ownership proof of residence or office as relevant, proof of business Shop Act License/MOA & AOA/GST registration/ITR, Partnership Deed etc.</p>
      <p>You may also be asked to furnish the following documents depending upon bank’s policy vis-à-vis the professional loan you’re applying for. 1 year’s ITR & Computation, 12 months banking, 2 years ITR & financials, 12 months banking or any other as per requirement.</p>
      <p class="pl-ser">Eligibility Criteria</p>
      <p>Different banks have different eligibility criteria to apply for professional loans. Some banks will require the professional applying for the loan to have a minimum of 5 years of work experience.</p>

      <p class="pl-ser"><strong>Checkout our other services:</strong></p><br>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div style="margin-bottom: 100px;" class="other-services">
        <%= link_to custom_credit_card_path, method: :get do %>
            <%= image_tag "icons/cc-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>
            Credit Card
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_transfer_personal_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/transfer-personal-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Transfer Personal Loan
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_business_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/business-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Business Loan
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_professional_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/professional-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Professional Loan
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_home_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/home-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Home Loan
        <%end%>
        <br><br><br>
        <%= link_to custom_transfer_home_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/tr-home-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Transfer Home Loan
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_loan_against_property_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/loan-against-property-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Loan Against Property
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_new_car_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/new-car-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          New Car Loan
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to custom_used_car_loan_path, method: :get do %>
          <%= image_tag "icons/used-car-loan-icon.svg", style: "width: 25px;" %>&nbsp;
          Used Car Loan
        <%end%>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

